---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Card from '@/components/ui/Card.astro'
import CardContent from '@/components/ui/CardContent.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Consulting - Portfolio"
  description="Strategic innovation consulting services across fintech, deep tech, and emerging technologies."
>
  <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">Consulting</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
        Strategic innovation and technology advisory
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Comic & Services Message -->
    <Card class="bg-accent/20 border-accent">
      <CardContent class="p-8 text-center">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <pre class="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-mono leading-tight">
{`    📊 "CONSULTING COMMAND CENTER" 📊
    
    ┌─────────────────────────────────┐
    │  👔 CLIENT: "We need to        │
    │     'synergize our blockchain   │
    │     AI metaverse strategy'"     │
    │                                 │
    │  🤔 CONSULTANT: "Let's start    │
    │     with: what problem are      │
    │     you actually solving?"      │
    │                                 │
    │  💡 EPIPHANY: *lightbulb        │
    │     appears*                    │
    │                                 │
    │  🎯 STRATEGY: "Oh! We need a    │
    │     better website."            │
    └─────────────────────────────────┘
    
    Real consulting in action:
    
      Problem → Analysis → Solution
         ↓         ↓         ↓
      📋       🔍       ⚡
      Chaos    Logic    Magic
    
      [STRATEGY.EXE] ✅
      [BULLSH*T.EXE] ❌`}
          </pre>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Services Under Development</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Comprehensive consulting portfolio being finalized. Services will cover DevOps architecture, 
          developer relations strategy, business development, and strategic technology advisory for 
          emerging fintech and deep tech ventures.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-8">
          <div class="text-left">
            <p>🏗️ DevOps & Infrastructure</p>
            <p>🤝 Developer Relations</p>
            <p>📈 Business Development</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-left">
            <p>🎯 Strategic Technology Advisory</p>
            <p>⚡ Innovation Architecture</p>
            <p>🔄 System Optimization</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="mailto:avalidurl@pm.me?subject=Consulting Inquiry" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-md hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors font-medium"
          >
            Get in Touch →
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/portfolio" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-input bg-background hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground rounded-md transition-colors font-medium"
          >
            ← Back to Portfolio
          </a>
        </div>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
